thread.title: Juanita Wells
thread.title_full: Public Storage reviewed by Juanita Wells

author: Juanita Wells
title: Juanita Wells
text: Everything was great when i got the storage unit the lady that helped was really awesome but a couple nights later when i went to put my stuff in storage, it was so dark and i went to turn on the light in the unit and it didn't work. Then I just by chance i had another new bulb on me so I changed the bulbs only to find out it still didn't work so we were trying to load the unit with no light at all. Very disappointed.
